President of Olympic Committee of Bosnia and Herzegovina: firmly believe that China has the ability to run a good winter Olympic event at a special time - Xinhua Xinhua Sarajevo, Dec. 11 (Xinhua) -- President of Olympic Committee of Bosnia and Herzegovina Kvesic recently said that Bosnia and Herzegovina is very much looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and firmly believe that China has the ability to run a good winter Olympic event at a special time. Recently, Chinese Ambassador to Bosnia and Herzegovina Ji Ping met with President of the Olympic Committee of Bosnia and Herzegovina Kvesic at the Olympic Center in Sarajevo. During the meeting, Mr. Kvesic commented positively on the relationship between Bosnia and China and said that he had visited China on the occasion of the 2008 Summer Olympics in Beijing and was very impressed by the excellent organization work of the Chinese side, firmly believing that China has the ability to run the Winter Olympics in a special period; Bosnia and Herzegovina is looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and the Olympic Committee of Bosnia and Herzegovina is actively organizing its participation; Bosnia and Herzegovina hopes to take this opportunity to carry out more extensive exchanges and cooperation with China in the field of sports. Ji Ping said that China and Bosnia have a special "Olympic bond". The 1984 Winter Olympic Games in Sarajevo were successfully held here, and in two months, the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympic Games will also kick off, presenting a simple, safe and wonderful event to the world. The Chinese Embassy in Bosnia and Herzegovina is willing to continue to play a bridging role and take the Beijing Winter Olympic Games as an opportunity to promote the deepening of humanistic exchanges between the two countries, so that the two peoples can "reach the future together" and wish the athletes of Bosnia and Herzegovina good results in Beijing. Before the meeting, the Olympic Committee of Bosnia and Herzegovina held an award ceremony for the "10th Sportsman of the Year", and Ji Ping was invited as a special guest to present the award to the best young sportsman of Bosnia and Herzegovina. The event played the Beijing Winter Olympic Games promotional video on a loop.
